    $(document).ready(function(){
 	var homeSlider = {
 		banners:null,
 		index:0,
 		init:function(banners){
 			homeSlider.banners = banners;
 			if(homeSlider.banners.length > 0){
 				homeSlider.slider();
 			}
 		},
 		slider:function(){
 			if(undefined === homeSlider.banners[homeSlider.index]){
 				homeSlider.index = 0;
 			}
 			var item = homeSlider.banners[homeSlider.index];
 			$('#main-banner').children('a').addClass('place');
 			$('#main-banner').children('a').attr('href',item.href).html('<img class="main-banner-img" src="'+item.image+'">')
 			$('#main-banner').children('a').removeClass('place');
 			homeSlider.index++;
 			setTimeout(function(){homeSlider.slider();},5000);
 		}
 	}
 	homeSlider.init([{"href":"javascript:;","image":"http:\/\/res.wiwaa.com\/image\/cache\/catalog\/main-banner\/1-1920x550.jpg","new_window":0},{"href":"javascript:;","image":"http:\/\/res.wiwaa.com\/image\/cache\/catalog\/main-banner\/2-1920x550.jpg","new_window":0}])
